        },
        {
          "from": "IfxGtm_Tom_PwmHl_setDeadtime / DTM-specific setup",
          "to": "Configure complementary outputs and 1 µs rising/falling dead-time via IfxGtm_Pwm config (TOM1/DTM backed)",
